title: Ace Attorney Investigations (2) - Prosecutor's Path
description:
Gyakuten Kenji 2
Ace Attorney Investigations (2) - Prosecutor's Path


The game was never released outside of Japan, but fortunately, some fans have translated the entire game in English. 


Get the English patch here: http://gbatemp.net/threads/ace-attorney-investigation-2-prosecutors-path-release-cases-1-3.354917/ 


They also have directions on how to apply the patch to the rom.


This is the Japanese version; you'll have to download the patch at the URL I provided and apply it to the ROM.
